text: County Road 27 () is a county road which runs between Ringebu and Folldal. The length of the road is 82.7 km, of which 26.1 km in the former Oppland and 56.6 km in the former Hedmark. Previously, County Road 27 continued from Enden to Atna in Stor-Elvdal, the stretch between Enden and Ringebu was signposted highway 220.Cappelens bil- og turistkart, dobbeltblad 3-4 (1982) ==References== 027 Category:Roads in Innlandet Category:National Tourist Routes in Norway
